window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>There's never been a time when I haven't been in love with Yelena Melnikov.</b></p> <p><b>Valentin</b></p> <p>She was a temptation that I was powerless to resist. I gave her my heart when we were kids, knowing we'd have to hide our love. We hid it for years until one night of careless passion led to a pregnancy.</p> <p>For me, this changes nothing. Yelena as my wife, Yelena as the mother of my childrenâ€¦ that was always the plan.</p> <p>I thought telling our family would be the hardest part. I've never been more wrong in my life.</p> <p><b>Yelena</b></p> <p>Val has always had my heart. I thought telling our family would be the hardest thing we'd ever have to go through.</p> <p>I was wrong. What we're about to face is so much worse.</p> <p>All I ever wanted was Valentin Melnikov as my husband and a houseful of kids, but now someone is threatening to take all that away from us, and I'm not sure we're going to survive it.</p> <p><i>This is a very steamy dark mafia romance with some humor mixed in! This is the fourth book in the Devils Will Rise: Melnikov Legacy series of interconnected standalones. No cheating, no OW drama, and an HEA are always guaranteed! For mature listeners.</i></p>"; 
